---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="For Streaming Platforms">
    <main>
        <div class="hero">
            <h1>For Streaming Platforms: The Series That Transcends Entertainment Categories</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Captivate subscribers with a groundbreaking original that blends nostalgia, innovation, and binge-worthy storytelling</p>
        </div>

        <section class="content">
            <div class="info-card vision">
                <h2>The Streaming Opportunity</h2>
                <p>"Living with the Ghost of Sam" represents the rare content proposition that solves multiple strategic challenges facing streaming platforms today: it captures nostalgic appeal while delivering cutting-edge concept, creates multi-generational co-viewing opportunities, and offers a fresh approach to IP development in an increasingly competitive marketplace.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card platform-benefits">
                <h2>Platform-Specific Advantages</h2>
                <p>This series delivers key benefits that align perfectly with streaming service priorities:</p>
                
                <div class="highlight-box">
                    <h3>Subscriber Acquisition & Retention</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Appeals to comedy fans across all demographic groups</li>
                        <li>Attracts tech-forward viewers interested in AI concepts</li>
                        <li>Creates nostalgia-driven subscription motivation for Gen X and Boomers</li>
                        <li>Builds organic social media conversation through its innovative premise</li>
                        <li>Offers evergreen appeal through timeless comedy connections</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card content-strategy">
                <h2>Strategic Content Differentiation</h2>
                <div class="two-column">
                    <div>
                        <h3>Category-Defying Appeal:</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Supernatural mystery drives initial viewer engagement</li>
                            <li>Comedy nostalgia creates emotional connection</li>
                            <li>Technology elements appeal to forward-thinking audiences</li>
                            <li>Character-driven drama ensures sustained investment</li>
                            <li>Multi-layered storytelling rewards repeat viewing</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Algorithm-Friendly Attributes:</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Cross-categorization increases discovery opportunities</li>
                            <li>Episode structure balances serialization with standalone elements</li>
                            <li>Strong thematic tags for recommendation engines</li>
                            <li>Both new and established talent to feature in promotions</li>
                            <li>Visual distinctiveness for thumbnail effectiveness</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card flexibility">
                <h2>Production & Release Flexibility</h2>
                <p>Designed with streaming economics in mind:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Scalable production approach allows for budget optimization</li>
                    <li>Primary mansion setting creates production efficiency</li>
                    <li>Episode structures adaptable for weekly or binge release models</li>
                    <li>Self-contained first season with clear continuation opportunities</li>
                    <li>Episodes buildable as 30, 45, or 60-minute formats depending on platform preference</li>
                    <li>Modular VFX approach allows for scaling based on performance</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card universe">
                <h2>Expandable Universe Potential</h2>
                <p>Beyond the initial series, "Living with the Ghost of Sam" offers rich opportunities for platform-exclusive expansion:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Digital shorts featuring individual comedian "ghosts" for social media and supplemental content</li>
                    <li>Documentary companion series exploring the real-life legacies of featured comedians</li>
                    <li>Interactive elements allowing viewers to explore the mansion's secrets</li>
                    <li>AR/VR experiences extending the concept to emerging platform technologies</li>
                    <li>Spin-off potential following different comedic legacies or time periods</li>
                    <li>Gaming and metaverse adaptation opportunities</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card seasons">
                <h2>Multi-Season Vision</h2>
                <p>A clear path for sustained engagement:</p>
                <div class="season-grid">
                    <div class="season-card">
                        <h3>Season 1: Discovery</h3>
                        <p>Derek and Nancy uncover the mansion's secrets and confront the Blackwood family's initial attempts to control the technology, culminating in a performance that protects the comedians' digital consciousness.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="season-card">
                        <h3>Season 2: Expansion</h3>
                        <p>The couple launches the Laugh Asylum comedy club while discovering deeper truths about the mansion's quantum technology and its connections to other entertainment venues worldwide.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="season-card">
                        <h3>Season 3: Confrontation</h3>
                        <p>A global technology corporation attempts to weaponize the consciousness-preservation system, forcing Derek and Nancy to build alliances with unexpected partners to protect all digital legacies.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card audience-data">
                <h2>Audience & Market Analysis</h2>
                <p>Data-driven approach to audience targeting:</p>
                <div class="stats-grid">
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-number">85%</div>
                        <p>Of streaming subscribers express interest in nostalgic content with modern twists</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-number">67%</div>
                        <p>Of 18-34 demographic shows strong interest in AI-themed entertainment</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-number">74%</div>
                        <p>Of comedy content viewers regularly share and discuss shows on social media</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-number">3.2x</div>
                        <p>Higher completion rate for series with supernatural elements compared to industry average</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card materials">
                <h2>Available Assets</h2>
                <div class="materials-grid">
                    <a href={`${base}scripts`} class="material-link">
                        <div class="material-card">
                            <h3>Complete Scripts</h3>
                            <p>All ten episodes of Season 1</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href={`${base}bible`} class="material-link">
                        <div class="material-card">
                            <h3>Series Bible</h3>
                            <p>World-building and character development</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href={`${base}analytics`} class="material-link">
                        <div class="material-card">
                            <h3>Audience Analytics</h3>
                            <p>Target demographic data and engagement projections</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href={`${base}universe`} class="material-link">
                        <div class="material-card">
                            <h3>Universe Blueprint</h3>
                            <p>Five-year expansion plan across formats</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card contact">
                <h2>Ready to Secure Your Platform's Next Original Hit?</h2>
                <p>Schedule a presentation with our team to explore how "Living with the Ghost of Sam" can become your platform's signature series.</p>
                <a href="mailto:contact@example.com" class="contact-btn">Request Executive Presentation</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    main {
        color: white;
    }

    .hero {
        background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)), url('/living-with-the-ghost-of-sam/images/SamImage.jpg') no-repeat center center;
        background-size: cover;
        padding: 4rem 2rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .hero h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin: 0;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    .subtitle {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        opacity: 0.9;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    .content {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem;
    }

    .info-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .info-card h2 {
        color: #FFD700;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .info-card h3 {
        color: #FFD700;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .info-card ul {
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .info-card li {
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .highlight-box {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .highlight-box h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
    }

    .two-column {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    .season-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .season-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .season-card h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
    }

    .stats-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .stat-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        text-align: center;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .stat-number {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #FFD700;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .materials-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .material-link {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: inherit;
    }

    .material-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        transition: transform 0.2s, background-color 0.2s;
    }

    .material-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }

    .contact {
        text-align: center;
    }

    .contact-btn {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #2196F3;
        color: white;
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        border-radius: 4px;
        text-decoration: none;
        margin-top: 1rem;
        transition: background-color 0.2s;
    }

    .contact-btn:hover {
        background: #1976D2;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .two-column, .season-grid, .stats-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .materials-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }
</style>
